---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Loan EMI Payment Online | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="/pages/recharge-bills">Recharge &amp; Bills</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>Loan EMI Payment</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Loan EMI Payment Online</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Pay your loan EMIs on time for all major banks and NBFCs from one platform. Instant confirmation, payment reminders, and complete payment history.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-building-columns"></i> Lenders: 50+ Banks &amp; NBFCs
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Confirmation: Instant
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-bell"></i> Due Date Reminders
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>Never Miss a Loan EMI Again</h2>
          <p>TrueCred Loan Expert provides a centralized platform to pay all your loan EMIs online — personal loans, home loans, car loans, business loans, education loans, and more. Whether your loan is with a public sector bank, private bank, or an NBFC, you can pay the EMI in seconds from our platform.</p>
          <p>Timely EMI payments are critical for maintaining a healthy CIBIL score. With TrueCred, you can set up payment reminders, view upcoming due dates for all your loans in one place, and pay instantly via UPI, net banking, or card. Never worry about late fees or credit score drops again.</p>

          <!-- Supported Lenders Table -->
          <h3>Supported Banks &amp; NBFCs</h3>
          <div class="table-responsive" style="overflow-x:auto; margin: 24px 0 40px;">
            <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; min-width:600px;">
              <thead>
                <tr style="background: var(--primary); color: #fff;">
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:left;">Lender</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:left;">Loan Types</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">Auto-Pay</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">Instant Receipt</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">SBI</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Personal, Home, Car, Education, Gold</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #f9fafb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">HDFC Bank</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Personal, Home, Car, Business, LAP</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">ICICI Bank</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Personal, Home, Car, Education, Gold</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #f9fafb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Bajaj Finserv</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Personal, Business, Home, Doctor Loan</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Tata Capital</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Personal, Business, Home, Consumer Durable</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Axis Bank</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px;">Personal, Home, Car, Education, Gold</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Yes</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p style="color:#6b7280; font-size: 0.9rem;">* 50+ banks and NBFCs are supported. The table shows select popular lenders.</p>

          <!-- Benefits -->
          <h2>Why Pay EMIs Through TrueCred?</h2>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>All Lenders in One Place:</strong> Pay EMIs for SBI, HDFC, ICICI, Bajaj Finserv, Tata Capital, Axis, and 50+ more lenders</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Protect Your CIBIL Score:</strong> On-time EMI payments keep your credit score healthy — track due dates and get reminders</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Instant Payment Confirmation:</strong> Get real-time payment receipt and confirmation via SMS and email</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Due Date Reminders:</strong> Set up SMS and email reminders before each EMI due date so you never miss a payment</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Part-Payment Support:</strong> Make partial prepayments towards your loan principal to reduce overall interest burden</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Complete Payment History:</strong> View and download all EMI payment receipts for tax filing and record-keeping</li>
          </ul>

          <!-- How It Works -->
          <h2>How to Pay Your Loan EMI</h2>
          <p>Pay your loan EMI in 4 simple steps.</p>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Select Your Lender</h4>
              <p>Choose the bank or NBFC where you have an active loan from our supported lenders list.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Enter Loan Account Number</h4>
              <p>Enter your loan account number or registered mobile number to fetch your EMI details.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Verify &amp; Pay</h4>
              <p>Review the EMI amount and due date, then pay via UPI, net banking, or debit/credit card.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Payment Confirmed</h4>
              <p>Receive instant payment confirmation and downloadable receipt via SMS and email.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Page CTA -->
          <div class="page-cta">
            <div>
              <h3>Looking to Refinance Your Loan?</h3>
              <p>Compare balance transfer offers from top lenders and save on interest with lower EMIs.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/pages/personal-loan" class="btn btn-outline">Compare Loans <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <!-- EMI Payment Form -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign" style="color: var(--primary); margin-right: 6px;"></i> Pay Loan EMI</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input">
                  <option value="">Select Lender / Bank</option>
                  <option value="sbi">SBI</option>
                  <option value="hdfc">HDFC Bank</option>
                  <option value="icici">ICICI Bank</option>
                  <option value="axis">Axis Bank</option>
                  <option value="bajaj">Bajaj Finserv</option>
                  <option value="tata">Tata Capital</option>
                  <option value="kotak">Kotak Mahindra Bank</option>
                  <option value="pnb">Punjab National Bank</option>
                  <option value="other">Other Lender</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input">
                  <option value="">Select Loan Type</option>
                  <option value="personal">Personal Loan</option>
                  <option value="home">Home Loan</option>
                  <option value="car">Car Loan</option>
                  <option value="business">Business Loan</option>
                  <option value="education">Education Loan</option>
                  <option value="gold">Gold Loan</option>
                  <option value="lap">Loan Against Property</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Loan Account Number">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="number" class="form-input" placeholder="EMI Amount (₹)">
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
                Pay EMI Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Links -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Other Services</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/mobile-recharge"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Mobile Recharge</a>
              <a href="/pages/electricity-bill"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Electricity Bill Payment</a>
              <a href="/pages/dth-recharge"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> DTH Recharge</a>
              <a href="/pages/fastag-recharge"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> FASTag Recharge</a>
              <a href="/pages/lpg-gas-booking"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> LPG Gas Booking</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Free Credit Score</a>
              <a href="/pages/calculators"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> EMI Calculator</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">FAQs</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Common questions about loan EMI payments on TrueCred.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Which banks and NBFCs can I pay loan EMIs for?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              TrueCred supports EMI payments for 50+ banks and NBFCs including SBI, HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank, Axis Bank, Punjab National Bank, Kotak Mahindra Bank, Bajaj Finserv, Tata Capital, Muthoot Finance, Manappuram Finance, L&amp;T Finance, Piramal Finance, and many more. If your lender accepts BBPS payments, you can pay through TrueCred.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Will my EMI payment reflect immediately with my lender?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              EMI payments made through TrueCred are processed via the Bharat Bill Payment System (BBPS) and typically reflect with your lender within 1-2 business days. You will receive an instant payment confirmation from TrueCred, and a separate confirmation from your lender once they process the payment. We recommend paying 2-3 days before the due date for timely credit.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Can I make a part-payment or prepayment on my loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, TrueCred supports part-payments/prepayments for select lenders. You can enter a custom amount higher than your regular EMI to make a part-payment towards your loan principal. This can help reduce your overall interest burden and loan tenure. Check if your lender allows part-payments without foreclosure charges before proceeding.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Does paying EMI through TrueCred affect my CIBIL score?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Paying your EMI through TrueCred has the same positive effect as paying directly through your lender. The payment is routed to your lender via the official BBPS system, so it counts as a regular on-time payment. In fact, using TrueCred's reminders can help you maintain perfect payment discipline, which positively impacts your CIBIL score.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Where do I find my loan account number?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Your loan account number is mentioned in your loan agreement, sanction letter, and monthly EMI statement from your lender. You can also find it in your lender's mobile app or internet banking under the loans section. If you're unable to locate it, contact your lender's customer service. On TrueCred, you can also try looking up your account using your registered mobile number.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
